---
title: Korean-Style Tofu, Beef & Garlic Rice with Sesame Veggies & Plant-Based Mayo
description: If you're familiar with bibimbap, the Korean “mixed rice” dish, then you'll love this HelloFresh plant-based version.So, divvy up the fragrant rice, pile on the tofu and toppings, then mix it all together for a glorious fusion of flavours and textures.

